By: Rand Fishkin October 31, 2005 SEOmoz Ranking Factors in 3rd Place Moz News The author's views are entirely their own (excluding the unlikely event of hypnosis) and may not always reflect the views of Moz. Our ranking factors article from several weeks ago is now in 3rd place at del.icio.us SEO tags for all time most popular. 671 folks have tagged it to date and we're closing in on Vaughn's Google Ranking Factors List, which is several years old but has been diligently updated. Not that I follow this kind of thing... FYI; SEOmoz's next article will most likely be an in-depth overview and introduction to SEO. We've been getting a lot of visitors and contacts who need a basic primer on the subject and it's time I delivered. Copied! Back to Top
